error_thread_notfound: Could not load thread. The post may have been deleted or you may have blocked/blocking by the root posting user.
profiles_description: All pages other than the TOP page (profile page, search, etc.) are accessed via the main account. Profile pages on a server different from the main account cannot be accessed. This will be improved in the future.
push_toggle_switch_this_account: Enable push notifications for this account
profile_account_missing_title: No account is set up in the workspace
column_account_missing_text_1: {name} has not been added to the workspace in use. Please add it from the workspace settings or delete the column.
column_account_missing_text_2: Unknown handle column. This column is no longer available due to an update, please remove and re-add.
bookmark_add_description: Bookmarks are saved locally in the browser. Data may be lost by clearing the cache, etc.
list_add_description: Lists are stored locally in the browser. Data may be lost by clearing the cache, etc.
no_account_in_profile: No account is set up in the workspace
no_account_in_profile_description: One or more accounts must be added to the workspace.
darkmode_disabled_theme: The dark mode setting has no effect on the theme in use.
color_disabled_theme: Color is disabled for the theme in use.
theme_code_description: You can install a limited theme by entering the corresponding code.
missing_accounts_description: Some accounts require re-authentication. Please login again or logout.
official_list_add_description: The list is created on Bluesky. It is public data and can be viewed by anyone.
repost_confirm_text_1: Quotations can be made via the
skip_delete_confirm: Do not check when deleting a post
login_box_text_1_2: browser client with multi-column and multi-account support.
login_box_text_2: It is PWA compliant and can be used like an app on mobile devices.
reaction_other_account: Select the account in the workspace
auto_refresh_realtime_notice: Real-time updates will increase communication traffic. Use with mobile data connection is not recommended.Acquisition omissions and back and forth time series may occur.
link_warning_confirm_title: Do you want to open the link?
skip_link_warning_confirm: Do not check for transitions to links that differ from the text
ai_alt_note: If you use AI to generate ALT text, please keep in mind that the image will be sent to an external server for analysis. This application is not responsible for the results generated.
error_missing_parameter_account: Invalid URL. Not a logged-in account.
keyword_mute_description:
To apply the changes to an existing post, refresh the page.
Settings are saved locally.
there_is_no_list_member:
List member is empty.
Let's add a member from the user search.
active_columns_description: You can also pinch and reorder.
welcome_to_tokimeki_text1:
First, let's choose a layout.
(You can change it at any time)
welcome_to_tokimeki_text2:
You can add columns for notifications, custom feeds, etc. using the + button in the upper left corner.
If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us @tokimeki.blue.
layout_single_description: This mode displays a single column on the screen, just like the official client. Recommended for beginners.
layout_decks_description: This mode allows multiple columns to be displayed side by side on the screen. Recommended for advanced users who want to check many timelines and notifications at a glance.
theme_store_supporter_recommend_1: âœ¨Limited theme for supporters is distributed at
thread_gate_reset_when_change_account: The reply limit setting has been reset due to a change in the posting account.
thread_gate_nobody_label: Nobody can reply to this post
thread_gate_modal_description: Select an account to which you can reply to this post.
advanced_break_title: Experimental: Advanced line break control for Japanese
advanced_break_description: Enables natural folding using machine learning. Only Chrome and Edge browsers are supported.
settings_embed_description: Turn on/off embedding of YouTube, Twitter, etc.
reaction_button_settings_description: Settings to turn on/off the Like button, etc. and hide numbers
server_status_minor: There may be a problem with the Bluesky server.
server_status_major: There is a problem with the Bluesky server.
success_repost_mute: Reposts by this user will not be displayed. Posts that are already displayed will be applied after reloading.
success_repost_unmute: Displays reposts by this user. Posts already displayed will be applied after reloading.
mod_list_cover_title: This list is the moderation list
mod_list_cover_text: Created by the creator for the purpose of collectively muting or blocking users.
mod_list_notice_temp: Here is a list of the main accounts for the current workspace.
bookmark_export_description: Download bookmark and draft data stored on the current browser.
bookmark_import_description: Import bookmark and draft data into this browser.
bookmark_import_warning: When an import is executed, all bookmark and draft data on the current browser will be deleted. If the import fails, the previous data cannot be restored.
bookmark_import_error: Failed to import bookmarks and drafts
post_mute_success: Post is hidden. This is only valid on this device (browser).
bluefeed_feeds_not_found: No Bluefeed feeds created were found.
bluefeed_add_duplicate: This post has already been added to the feed.
mute_keywords_import_description: Imports text and hashtags without distinction
global_label_settings_description: This applies to self-labeling posts, etc. Other similar labels may be defined for each labeler.
official_label_settings_description: Applies to labels by Bluesky Moderation Service.
labeler_description: Labeler subscription settings are separate from the official application and are stored locally. The same labeler is applied to all accounts.
self_labeling_note: Self-labeling is only valid for posts with media.
delete_and_edit_confirm_description: Existing reactions will be lost. The reply tree will not be taken over.
success_to_delete_and_edit: Posts have been restored to the edit screen.
chat_settings_description: Chat incoming settings are stored on the Bluesky server for each account. It does not affect chats that have already been started.
error_chat_incoming_disabled: Chat cannot be sent to this user.
app_password_scope_error: You do not have permission to access chat. You will need to log in again with the app password that "Allow access to your direct messages".
settings_about_description: Updates are hosted by WhiteWind, a blogging service provided by AT Protocol.
detach_information: Show only to: You have detached the quote. You can undo it from the menu.
success_un_detach: The detached quote has been restored.
error_video_too_large: Video is too big or too long! You can upload videos up to 100 MB and no longer than 180 seconds.
bookmark_cloud_add_description: Cloud bookmarks are stored on the TOKIMEKI server and can be used on other devices.
font_theme_notice: Due to performance issues, Web fonts are not available in your browser.
atmosphere_description:
Here is a list of Atmosphere services used by this user.
AT Protocol allows you to create and publish various services in addition to Bluesky.
You can hide them from the Settings -> General.
login_2fa_code_send: The two-factor authentication code has been sent to your e-mail address. Please confirm and enter the code.
bluecast_nothing: There is no live at this time.
lossless_image_upload_mode_notice: If the image size is larger than 1MB, an error will occur and you will not be able to post. An error may also occur if the image format is not JPG/PNG.
